#Python software reference for a separable 2D convolution filter for an image
# Utilizes Python Imaging Library (PIL).  By default in Python2.7 in Ubuntu.  
# Otherwise need to download at pythonware.com/products/pil/

Usage: %s <inputImageFile> <inputFilterFile> <outputImageFile> <optional:outputAsciiPixelFile>

Example:
python gaussianFilter.py blurFilter.txt Lena.jpg Lena_blur.jpg
